{"lemma":"سَفْحُ","slug":"سَفْحُ","root":"س.ف.ح","root_slug":"س-ف-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ف-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19906","n19907","n19910"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%92%D8%AD%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pour, to flow"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to spill, to shed","examples":[{"text":"إِنِّي وَجَدِّكَ مَا هَجَوْتُكَ وَٱلْأَنْصَابُ يُسْفَحُ بَيْنَهُنَّ دَمُ"},{"text":"إِلَّا أَنْ يَكُونَ مَيْتَةً أَوْ دَمًا مَسْفُوحًا أَوْ لَحْمَ خِنْزِيرٍ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَفَحَ (safaḥa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bottom"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"foot (of a mountain)","examples":[{"text":"فَإِذَا نَزَلْتُمْ بِعَدُوٍّ، أَوْ نَزَلَ بِكُمْ، فَلْيَكُنْ مُعَسْكَرُكُمْ فِي قُبُلِ الأَشْرَافِ، وَأَسْفَاحِ الجِبَالِ، وَأَثْنَاءِ الأَنْهَارِ"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19906","headword_ar":"سَفَحَ","root":"sfH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safoHN","text_ar":"سَفْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) [and app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufuwHN","text_ar":"سُفُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, mentioned in what follows,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He poured out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"water: (S, A:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he shed"},{"kind":"text","text":"blood, (S, A, Msb, K,) the blood of another; (S, A;) and tears; (Msb, K;) inf. n. as above, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufuwHN","text_ar":"سُفُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaHati AlEayonu damoEahaA","text_ar":"سَفَحَتِ العَيْنُ دَمْعَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the eye shed its tears"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) The saying, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faqatala EalaYraA^osi AlmaA='i Hat~aY","text_ar":"فَقَتَلَ عَلَىرَاْسِ المَا=ءِ حَتَّى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaHa Ald~amu AlmaA='a","text_ar":"سَفَحَ الدَّمُ المَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been explained as meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And he slew at the head of the water so that"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the blood covered the water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but IAth says that this is not consistent with the language; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safoHN","text_ar":"سَفْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the act of “ pouring out, or forth; ” and that the meaning may therefore be, that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the blood made the water to pour forth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as when, into a full vessel, something heavier than what is in it is poured; for in this case there comes forth from it as much as has been poured into it. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufiHa fiY AlA^arDi","text_ar":"سُفِحَ فِى الاَرضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was stretched,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extended, upon the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"], said of a camel. (K.)       -A2-  The verb is also used intransitively; you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaHa","text_ar":"سَفَحَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaA='u","text_ar":"المَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~amoEu","text_ar":"الدَّمْعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufuwHN","text_ar":"سُفُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaHaAnN","text_ar":"سَفَحَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safoHN","text_ar":"سَفْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tears,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poured out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K","O"]},{"entry_id":"n19907","headword_ar":"سفّح","root":"sfH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasofiyHN","text_ar":"تَسْفِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did a deed that profited him not;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) likened to the arrow called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~afiH","text_ar":"السَّفِح"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n19910","headword_ar":"سَفْحٌ","root":"sfH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"base, foot, bottom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSol","text_ar":"اَصْل"},{"kind":"text","text":", K, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asofal","text_ar":"اَسْفَل"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, A, K,) of a mountain, (S, A, K,) which is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part whereinto is poured"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yusofaHu","text_ar":"يُسْفَحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the water"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the parts above"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part where the side"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rests upon the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S: [as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafoHN","text_ar":"صَفْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaroD","text_ar":"عَرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof, [see this word,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that rests its side upon the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDiyD","text_ar":"حَضِيض"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"low ground at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by, the base,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] thereof: (K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spreading part"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (A: [there said to be in this sense tropical; but why, I see not:]) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"face"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (Msb:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower, part thereof, where it is rugged:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 80:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufuwHN","text_ar":"سُفُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  [The pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufuwHN","text_ar":"سُفُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rocks that are soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and slippery."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","Msb","TA"]}]}}